::Battera::

She looked at the comp screen and saw that Terminess was dead, but that 
Vulois was alive.  Her eyes brightened at the thought of her friend still 
being alive.  But she didn't want to face him yet.  She was afraid that he 
might not forgive her.  He had every reason to not forgive her for her 
cowardly actions.
"No."
